  <div class="row">
    
    <div class="span6 section">  
  
      <h3>ABOUT THE OPEN CLIP ART LIBRARY</h3>

      <p>This project aims to create an archive of clip art that can be used for free for any use. All clip art submitted to the project should be waived of all rights, including copyright, according to the <a href="http://sharism.org/agreement/">âœ³ Sharism Sharing Agreement</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
  </div>
  
  <div class="row">

    <div class="span6 section">
      <h3 class="span6 section">Get in Touch</h3>
      If you like to get in touch with us write a mail to <a href="mailto:everyone@openclipart.org">everyone@openclipart.org</a>!
      Or join the <a href="http://freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/clipart">mailing list</a>. If you're interested in the projects history you can also browse the <a href="http://freedesktop.org/pipermail/clipart/">mailing list archive</a>. 
