      <h3 class="span6 section">Join Us</h3>
      <p>There are several ways to contribute to this project:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/participate#use-advocate">Just use and advocate our project</a></li>
        <li><a href="/participate#share-remix">Upload own clip art and remix existing clip art</a></li>
        <li><a href="/participate#become-librerian">Help maintaining content and report bugs</a>
        <li><a href="/participate#become-developer">Add features and remove bugs in the code</a>
      </ul>
    </div>
   
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span12 section">
      <h3 class="section">Live Chat</h3>
